Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:01:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,請便
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你們準備一張輪椅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 立刻準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大家早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,睡個好覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不過睡得還湊合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧你們 我睡得很香喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來母親的儀式好像要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也會去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,尚城不拒絕任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,無論何人都會給予他生活的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣一個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是為了讓大家開心才被呼喚來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼爾 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大家可以自由參加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是宗教嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡的人都是被母親的能力吸引過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,聚集在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人就是母親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來將要舉行和死者的會面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,死者?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,母親她可以與死人對話喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 這太扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有母親那種能力的人被稱為靈媒師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,靈媒師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,指的是死後世界與現世之間的媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就是半熟和全熟的中間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被選中的參加者請到顏之間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,去跟上那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 剛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,想看儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是用金繕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是為了復原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,注入新的生命讓它延續
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,才是我們的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,死者的儀式也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,死者無法復活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可是知曉死者想法的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可以借助大地大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,與死者連接並使對話成立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,然後倖存者將開始新的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這股氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大麻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那是大地大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,尚城的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,以大地大人作為媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以讓母親使用出能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,難道10歲的是他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不久將舉辦誕生10周年的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,佳惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳救了被海嘯捲走的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,密碼就在金庫的裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,替我活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直守護著妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這是父親的鐘錶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真也 喂 真也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你能聽到我說的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在倒塌的屋子裡我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,丟下我自己跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要是連你也死掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,像大峽谷一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這是琵琶湖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,湖底出現了一條巨大的裂縫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,水就流了進去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼多的水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想和爸爸說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,總之就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我認為不是誰都能夠參加儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 這裡能夠看到菲律賓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,開個玩笑 嚇到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 妳也笑起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大家來拍張照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那個儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎麼做才能被選上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,根據天啟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,請勿靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,信不信是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是某個男子的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,妳摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想要與死者見面請根據順序
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我在和母親講話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,母親一天只能會見三人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想休息的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那個女孩是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是七海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,剛 全部吃掉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我會吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這是哪裡的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,南斯拉夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小時候經常吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,多吃點多吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這是科索沃的名菜燉肉湯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnAvenir Next W1G\b1\pos(793,668)}Paçe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,新來的 來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,偏食對健康不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不想被胖子說健康問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了飯就去上學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡有學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有喔 雖然也就幾十個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,剛 步 今天開始去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大家要是想工作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也儘管說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,還有很多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在三角形abc中 邊bc為底邊時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,頂點a到底邊bc的垂線長度為三角形的高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好多大麻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,工作真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的就拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛很癢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,地震?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你是知道地震會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 不會這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,學校如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,日本人太多了很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,挑三揀四可不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,力士什錦火鍋 知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,力士吃的那個東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 你喜歡相撲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒興趣 大谷先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我是非常喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得我能成為職業力士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 只是身體大是贏不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,剛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,和爸爸對話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,摩斯電碼 隨便做了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸絕對看得見的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想聽爸爸的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕爸爸會胡言亂語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還有可能生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 反正你也猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,火好像熄滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我去借個打火機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了母親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我心中的陰霾已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是也要參加比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人都在說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要去派對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,據說是週末的派對 在今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我被邀請過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,已經熄滅了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,換你來吹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 著起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是沒熄滅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,頭髮長長了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 媽媽妳不去派對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不習慣去吵鬧的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是很想聽爸爸的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽不想聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因為沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,其實妳是想和那個人搞好關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因為妳想忘記關於爸爸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,步 請妳懂事點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我就是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙和前輩也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有不去派對的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,明明派對那麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾也讓自己休息一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax Relax
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你最想見的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 其實是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,吵架可不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能好好和她說就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,筋疲力盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,讓自己稍微放鬆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要是不撐著我就要崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就是這樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,現在也正處於這種時期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家鄉是南斯拉夫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我的國家和家庭都已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我還有這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你們也還在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,託妳的福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是我錄的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 好好看好好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是DJ KITE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,別擅自用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的唱片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,讓作者來刷碟更好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不能播放的唱片就只是個圓盤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,DJ春生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,春生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒有退路了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,再不開始觀眾就要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,解放自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,日本最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,靜候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,去那邊聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,已經接受母親的儀式了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我這裡有個可以插隊的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,和我親熱起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我這裡有後門可以讓妳走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這種就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不會弄疼妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,保證讓妳舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,神力女超人一擊就打倒了攻擊地球的異形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到你吸了大麻會變成那種小屁孩性格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,異形是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不立刻離開日本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那些有錢人好像都想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因為很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,即使失去了重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒有時間傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這太殘酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,悲傷也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣爸爸會生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,擦乾眼淚前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸經常說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為有連自己的國家和家庭都回不去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才得忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我以後再也不會哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要動 舉起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看樣子不是為了通知面會的時間而來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.85,0:22:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,果然在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,藥 藥
